Description: The Flight into Egypt, with Joseph pulling the donkey carrying Mary and Christ across a wooden bridge while an angel bends a palm tree for the Child to pluck dates. c.1520/50 Engraving
Bibliographic references: Bartsch / Le Peintre graveur (XV.16.4) (as School of Marcantonio)
Acquisition name: Bequeathed by: Sir Hans Sloane (With Philipe's blindstamp and HS on the verso)
